it should have been detected then.

142
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:03,120
But what if it was like
last night's banquet?

143
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,960
Do you mean...

144
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,440
Perhaps someone used the trick
to mix something in the food,

145
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,920
put poison in the banquet,

146
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,320
and killed your mother.

147
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,640
But these are all my guesses.

148
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:21,040
I should hurry up
and prepare the twelve dishes.

149
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,520
Then maybe we can get something

150
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,560
out of Mr. Cao.

151
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,800
Thank you.

152
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,520
What's with the formality?

153
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,000
You talk like a scholar.

154
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:33,280
