your proud and uninhibited manner.

155
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,320
Put yourself together.

156
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:43,120
(A Cha is more and more concerned
about He Lianyu.)

157
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,200
(I need to think of a plan.)

158
