167
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,280
Very good.

168
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:27,240
With truth and falsehood,
we can muddy the waters.

169
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,120
Listen,

170
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,280
I'd like

171
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,640
