172
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,440
I know you like A Cha.

173
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,880
And I have feelings for He Lianyu.

174
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,320
You are suggesting...

175
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,520
How about we help each other out?

176
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:47,400
(Although the princess is willful,)

177
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,880
(she is cute
and comes from a noble background.)

178
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:53,160
(She's indeed
a good choice for stirring things up.)

179
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,480
Deal.

180
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,520
Deal.

